Regex: .*The zone with id '[0-9a-zA-Z-]{36}' was not found.*

^ (\w{10})    # product ID
          (\w)        # processing stage flag
          (\w{3})     # originator ID
          (\d{8}) _   # start_day
          (\d{6}) _   # start_time
          (\d{8})     # duration
          (\w)        # phase id
          (\d{3}) _   # cycle number within phase
          (\d{5}) _   # relative orbit number within cycle
          (\d{5}) _   # absolute orbit number
          (\d{4})     # product file counter
          \. (\w\w)   # satellite ID
